[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会]]正式名称为第二十二届冬季奥林匹克运动会，是2014年2月7日至23日在俄罗斯[[索契|索契]]举办的一场冬季[[综合运动会|综合运动会]]。来自88个国家和地区的2873名运动员参加了7个[[奥运会项目|类别]]、15个大项、98个小项的角逐<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.olympic.org/sochi-2014-winter-olympics | title = Sochi 2014 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150928165535/http://www.olympic.org/sochi-2014-winter-olympics | publisher = International Olympic Committee | accessdate = 2015-09-29 | archivedate = 2015-09-28 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。最终，共有来自26个国家和地区的187名运动员赢得奖牌<ref>{{cite web | url = http://data.huffingtonpost.com/winter-olympics-sochi-2014 | title = 2014 Sochi Winter Olympics: Schedules, Medals, Results | work = The Huffington Post | accessdate = 2015-09-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150905061330/http://data.huffingtonpost.com/winter-olympics-sochi-2014 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-09-05 }}</ref>。[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会荷兰代表团|荷兰队]]在[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会竞速滑冰比赛|速度滑冰比赛]]中包揽[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会竞速滑冰比赛－男子500公尺|男子500米]]、[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会竞速滑冰比赛－男子5000公尺|男子5000米]]、{{link-en|男子10000米|Speed skating at the 2014 Winter Olympics – Men's 10,000 metres}}和{{link-en|女子1500米|Speed skating at the 2014 Winter Olympics – Women's 1500 metres}}4个项目的全部奖牌，刷新之前一国最多包揽两个项目奖牌的纪录<ref>{{cite news | title = Bergsma breaks Olympic record to lead fourth Dutch medal sweep | date = 2014-02-19 | newspaper = [[新华社|新华社]] | url = http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/sports/2014-02/19/c_133125438.htm | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150923061814/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/sports/2014-02/19/c_133125438.htm | accessdate = 2015-09-29 | archivedate = 2015-09-23 }}</ref>。

东道主[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会俄罗斯代表团|俄罗斯队]]原本以13枚金牌排在奖牌榜首位，追平[[1976年冬季奥林匹克运动会|1976年冬奥会]]上苏联的金牌数{{#tag:ref|俄罗斯从法律地位角度而言属于苏联的[[国家继承|继承国]]<ref>{{cite book | last = Bühler | first = Konrad G. | title = State Succession and Membership in International Organisations | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=Ty7NAG1Jl-8C&pg=PA161 | series = Legal Aspects of International Organisation Series | volume = Volume 38 | year = 2001 | publisher = Martinus Nijhoff Publishers | isbn = 9789041115539 | pages = 161–164 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200819234130/https://books.google.com/books?id=Ty7NAG1Jl-8C&pg=PA161 | archivedate = 2020-08-19 | access-date = 2015-09-29 }}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref>{{cite web | title = 1976 Innsbruck | url = http://olympic.ca/games/1976-innsbruck/#Medals | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150925090520/http://olympic.ca/games/1976-innsbruck/#Medals | publisher = Canadian Olympic Committee | accessdate = 2015-09-29 | archivedate = 2015-09-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，但是之後因為禁藥醜聞被剝奪13面獎牌，在2017年11月24日在俄羅斯被取消[[雪車|雪車]]兩面金牌以後，挪威成為獎牌榜首名，到2017年12月22日俄羅斯排名下降第四名<ref>{{cite web|title=1976 Innsbruck|url=http://www.olympic.ca/en/games/winter-olympics/1976-innsbruck/#Medals|publisher={{le|加拿大奧林匹克委員會|Canadian Olympic Committee}}|accessdate=2015-08-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324152749/http://www.olympic.ca/en/games/winter-olympics/1976-innsbruck/#Medals|archivedate=2012-03-24}}</ref>{{#tag:ref|另外3次分别是[[1932年冬季奥林匹克运动会|1932年]]的美国<ref name="us1932">{{cite web | url = http://www.olympic.org/uk/games/past/table_uk.asp?OLGT=2&OLGY=1932 | title = 1932 Lake Placid Winter Games | publisher = International Olympic Committee | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081125003633/http://www.olympic.org/uk/games/past/table_uk.asp?OLGT=2&OLGY=1932 | archivedate = 2008-11-25 | accessdate = 2008-11-25 }}</ref>，[[1952年冬季奥林匹克运动会|1952年]]的挪威<ref name="sr1952">{{cite web | url = http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/winter/1952/ | title = 1952 Oslo Winter Games | publisher = Sports Reference LLC | accessdate = 2015-09-29 | archivedate = 2020-04-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200417040522/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/winter/1952/ }}</ref>和[[2010年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2010年]]的加拿大<ref>{{cite web | url = http://espn.go.com/olympics/winter/2010/medals | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150923031743/http://espn.go.com/olympics/winter/2010/medals | archivedate = 2015-09-23 | title = Vancouver 2010 Winter Olympics–Medals | publisher = ESPN | accessdate = 2015-09-29 }}</ref>。|group="注"}}，但多數裁定於2018年1月底被[[国际体育仲裁院|国际体育仲裁院]]推翻，被判定有服用禁藥的28名運動員被撤除終身停賽令。另外被剝奪的13面獎牌中，有9面獎牌再度恢復，使俄羅斯在獎牌總數上又回到首名。<ref>{{cite news|title=Russia back to 1st in overall Sochi Olympics medal count after CAS ruling|url=https://www.rt.com/sport/417596-russia-first-place-olympics/|work=RT International|date=2018-02-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201122239/https://www.rt.com/sport/417596-russia-first-place-olympics/|archivedate=2018-02-01|accessdate=2018-02-01}}</ref>

[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会斯洛维尼亚代表团|斯洛文尼亚队]]在[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会高山滑雪比赛－女子滑降|女子高山滑雪]]项目中夺冠，这也是该国赢得的首枚冬奥会金牌，与此同时，这项比赛还出现了首次并列金牌，另一支夺冠队伍是[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会瑞士代表团|瑞士队]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Herman | first = Martyn | date = 2014-02-12 | title = Maze amazes as she wins Slovenia's first gold | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150706103144/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/02/12/us-olympics-alpineskiing-maze-idUSBREA1B0VD20140212 | archivedate = 2015-07-06 | newspaper = ''Reuters'' | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/02/12/us-olympics-alpineskiing-maze-idUSBREA1B0VD20140212 | location = Rosa Khutor, Russia | accessdate = 2015-09-29 }}</ref>。在[[国际奥林匹克委员会|国际奥林匹克委员会]]于2017年11月重新检测兴奋剂样本后，由于奖牌重新分配，[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会拉脱维亚代表团|拉脱维亚]]赢得了第一枚奥运金牌<ref>{{cite web | url = https://olympics.com/en/stories/news/amp/latvia-4man-bob-sochi-2014-olympic-gold-sigulda-ceremony/ | title = Gold at last for Latvia's Sochi 2014 four-man bobsleigh champions | author = Browne, Ken | date = 2020-02-19 | website = [[国际奥林匹克委员会|国际奥林匹克委员会]] | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-date = 2021-11-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211113001817/https://olympics.com/en/stories/news/amp/latvia-4man-bob-sochi-2014-olympic-gold-sigulda-ceremony/ }}</ref>。[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会意大利代表团|意大利]][[雪橇运动|雪橇]]选手[[阿明·策格勒|阿明·策格勒]]成为第一位连续参加6届冬奥会，并且每次都获得奖牌的运动员<ref>{{cite news | accessdate = 2015-09-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326072353/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/09/sports/olympics/the-winning-formula-of-luges-old-man.html?_r=0 | title = The Winning Formula of Luge’s ‘Old Man’ | date = 2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2015-03-26 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/09/sports/olympics/the-winning-formula-of-luges-old-man.html?_r=0 | work = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | author = Macur, Juliet | deadurl = no }}</ref>，全部6枚奖牌都是在[[冬季奥林匹克运动会雪橇比赛|男子雪橇个人赛]]中获得<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.olympic.org/armin-zoeggeler | title = Armin Zöggeler | publisher = International Olympic Committee | accessdate = 2015-09-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150908193631/http://www.olympic.org/armin-zoeggeler | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-09-08 }}</ref>。

荷兰速滑选手[[伊伦·伍斯特|伊伦·伍斯特]]获得5枚奖牌（2金3银），比其他任何运动员都多。俄罗斯[[短道速滑|短道速滑选手]][[维克多·安|维克多·安]]、[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会挪威代表团|挪威]][[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会越野滑雪比赛|越野滑雪运动员]][[玛丽特·比约根|玛丽特·比约根]]，以及[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会白俄罗斯代表团|白俄罗斯]][[冬季两项|冬季两项选手]][[达荷亚·多姆拉切娃|达荷亚·多姆拉切娃]]各赢得3枚金牌，并列为获金牌最多的运动员<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/winter/2014/ | title = 2014 Sochi Winter Games | publisher = Sports Reference LLC | accessdate = 2015-09-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150906195402/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/winter/2014/ | archivedate = 2015-09-06 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

== 奖牌榜 ==
[[File:Women's_downhill,_2014_Winter_Olympics,_podium.jpg|right]]项目奖牌得主，从左至右依次为：[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会斯洛维尼亚代表团|斯洛文尼亚队]]的[[蒂娜·马泽|蒂娜·马泽]]（金牌），[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会瑞士代表团|瑞士队]]的[[多米妮克·吉辛|多米妮克·吉辛]]（金牌）和瑞士队的[[拉拉·古特|拉拉·古特]]（铜牌），这也是冬季奥运会历史上首度出现并列金牌<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150906015706/http://www.olympic.org/olympic-results/sochi-2014/alpine-skiing/downhill-w | url = http://www.olympic.org/olympic-results/sochi-2014/alpine-skiing/downhill-w | title = Women's downhill results | publisher = International Olympic Committee | accessdate = 2015-09-29 | archivedate = 2015-09-06 }}</ref>。]]
[[File:Men's_5000m,_2014_Winter_Olympics,_Podium.jpg|right]]奖牌得主，从左至右分别是：[[扬·布洛克伊森|扬·布洛克伊森]]（银牌）、[[斯文·克雷默|斯文·克雷默]]（金牌）和[[约里特·贝尔赫斯马|约里特·贝尔赫斯马]]（铜牌），这也是[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会荷兰代表团|荷兰队]]包揽全部奖牌的4项比赛之一<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/winter-olympics/26056127 | title = Sochi 2014: Sven Kramer defends 5,000 m speed skating title | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2014-02-08 | accessdate = 2015-09-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140405043725/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/winter-olympics/26056127 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-04-05 }}</ref>。]]
